title: Week 10 preview & Bills vs. Jets recap
itunes:title: Week 10 preview & Bills vs. Jets recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – go game by game breaking down each Week 10 matchup. Then, the heroes bring in Conor Orr to help recap the Thursday night football game that saw the Bills hold off a late-game run from the Jets to improve to 5-4 . Plus, an honest discussion about Ray Lewis’s budding music career.
